5000|$|A {{second problem}} {{stems from the}} {{required}} polarization of the waves. ELF waves only propagate long distances in vertical polarization, with {{the direction of the}} magnetic field lines horizontal and the electric field lines vertical. [...] Vertically oriented antennas are required to generate vertically <b>polarized</b> <b>waves.</b> Even if sufficiently large conventional antennas could be built {{on the surface of the}} Earth, these would generate horizontally polarized, not vertically <b>polarized</b> <b>waves.</b>|$|R
